  "wpt": true,
  "wpt_descr": "These tests verify the functionality of XSLT. They will need to be changed/removed:\n\nhttps://wpt.fyi/results/dom/xslt",
  "webview_risks": "In the same way that this poses a compat risk on the open web, it poses a risk for WebView applications.",
